data.description: No backyard neighbors! New HVAC! Private Pool! Open living spaces and large primary bedroom! Welcome to 12311 Lusterleaf Dr. in Cypress, TX. This home features a new 16-seer HVAC system, recently-blown insulation, NEW luxury vinyl plank flooring, NEW stainless cooking appliances, and a private pool. Tower Oak Bend is Zoned to highly acclaimed Cy-Fair ISD and just minutes from Highway 290, 249, and the Grand Parkway. Neighborhood amenities include a shaded park, tennis courts, basketball courts, and a neighborhood pool. No MUD taxes. No previous flooding. No backyard neighbors. Schedule your tour today!
